00:24:24,700 --> 00:24:25,836
- Yeah,

408
00:24:25,860 --> 00:24:28,386
he was a jerk when you
two were my students

409
00:24:28,410 --> 00:24:29,696
and he was a bigger jerk

410
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:31,406
when I told him where he could stuff it,

411
00:24:31,430 --> 00:24:33,906
so yeah, he's still a jerk.

412
00:24:33,930 --> 00:24:35,536
- You what?

413
00:24:35,560 --> 00:24:36,560
- I quit.

414
00:24:37,630 --> 00:24:38,454
- You're kidding me.

415
00:24:38,478 --> 00:24:40,871
- You remember what that place is like.

416
00:24:40,895 --> 00:24:45,276
You get to be my age you ran
out of patience for politics.

417
00:24:45,300 --> 00:24:46,823
It's a young man's game now.

418
00:24:47,744 --> 00:24:49,516
And I could never get used to the idea

419
00:24:49,540 --> 00:24:52,376
that one of my former
students was now my boss.

420
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:54,756
- Wow, I had no idea.

421
00:24:54,780 --> 00:24:56,306
When did all this happen?

