00:25:29,660 --> 00:25:32,596
- Grimsvotn, quite a mess, so I hear.

438
00:25:32,620 --> 00:25:34,786
- It is, I was there.

439
00:25:34,810 --> 00:25:38,096
- And the word is you took
along a team of rugrats.

