00:28:21,400 --> 00:28:22,357
- Dr. Shepherd,

499
00:28:22,381 --> 00:28:24,326
are you saying that you
can accurately predict

500
00:28:24,350 --> 00:28:26,676
where and when these eruptions will occur?

501
00:28:26,700 --> 00:28:29,006
- Given the proper resources, yes.

502
00:28:29,030 --> 00:28:30,816
- Right now, all we're looking at

503
00:28:30,840 --> 00:28:32,866
are generalities, probability.

504
00:28:32,890 --> 00:28:35,839
The point here is what some
may see as a coincidence,

505
00:28:35,863 --> 00:28:39,296
I think is the earth trying
to tell us something.

506
00:28:39,320 --> 00:28:41,546
And in my experience, when that happens,

507
00:28:41,570 --> 00:28:43,320
it's usually a good idea to listen.

508
00:28:44,860 --> 00:28:46,276
- My apologies, gentlemen.

509
00:28:46,300 --> 00:28:49,169
- Peter, I believe,
you know William Kincaid

510
00:28:49,193 --> 00:28:51,245
from the US Geological Survey.

511
00:28:51,269 --> 00:28:52,797
- Our paths have crossed, yes.

512
00:28:52,821 --> 00:28:53,956
Would you like me to recap?

513
00:28:53,980 --> 00:28:56,226
- Thanks, but I'm sure
I'll be able to catch up.

514
00:28:56,250 --> 00:28:58,396
Please continue.

515
00:28:58,420 --> 00:29:01,736
- Basically, we're seeing a
massive increase in activity

516
00:29:01,760 --> 00:29:03,726
on a worldwide scale.

517
00:29:03,750 --> 00:29:04,986
Now, I don't believe

518
00:29:05,010 --> 00:29:07,316
that these are a succession
of random volcanic events.

519
00:29:07,340 --> 00:29:09,190
I think they're part of a pattern

520
00:29:09,214 --> 00:29:10,986
which, if ignored,

521
00:29:11,010 --> 00:29:12,336
could have serious consequences

522
00:29:12,360 --> 00:29:14,446
to the future of life on this planet.

523
00:29:14,470 --> 00:29:15,786
- Peter, tell me you're not here

524
00:29:15,810 --> 00:29:18,276
to sell us this Exodus crap again.

