00:29:24,170 --> 00:29:25,579
- It's anything but half baked.

529
00:29:25,603 --> 00:29:27,556
- What Dr. Shepherd is suggesting

530
00:29:27,580 --> 00:29:29,386
runs contrary to theories

531
00:29:29,410 --> 00:29:30,906
