00:30:13,563 --> 00:30:15,706
that has caused the core's expansion?

550
00:30:15,730 --> 00:30:17,806
Or does your theory not cover that?

551
00:30:17,830 --> 00:30:19,936
- It could be any number
of different things.

552
00:30:19,960 --> 00:30:22,693
What is causing the pattern
