553
00:30:22,717 --> 00:30:24,766
Look, we can figure that out later,

554
00:30:24,790 --> 00:30:27,236
right now we need to
figure out how to stop it.

555
00:30:27,260 --> 00:30:29,086
- Dr. Shepherd,

556
00:30:29,110 --> 00:30:31,756
I'm afraid I just don't see the emergency.

557
00:30:31,780 --> 00:30:32,980
- How else can I put it?

558
00:30:34,081 --> 00:30:37,936
There are 1,500 volcanoes
