some of them are dormant.

560
00:30:40,294 --> 00:30:44,736
Over 150 of them are located
in North America alone.

561
00:30:44,760 --> 00:30:47,067
If they erupt, and I think they will.

562
00:30:47,091 --> 00:30:50,506
We are looking at cataclysmic devastation.

563
00:30:50,530 --> 00:30:51,716
- What's your worst case scenario?

564
00:30:51,740 --> 00:30:53,776
- Gentlemen, I think
it's my duty to point out

565
00:30:53,800 --> 00:30:55,759
that none of Dr.
Shepherd's so-called theory

566
00:30:55,783 --> 00:30:56,946
has yet to be proven.

567
00:30:56,970 --> 00:30:58,086
- Dr. Kincaid-

568
00:30:58,110 --> 00:30:59,186
- He could be completely wrong.

569
00:30:59,210 --> 00:31:01,760
- Please allow Dr. Shepherd
to answer the question.

570
00:31:03,770 --> 00:31:05,023
- Worst case scenario,

571
00:31:07,140 --> 00:31:09,780
the extinction of everything
living on the planet.

572
00:31:11,482 --> 00:31:13,096
- How long do we have?

573
00:31:13,120 --> 00:31:14,120
- Months?

574
00:31:15,380 --> 00:31:17,486
- Thank you, Dr. Shepherd,

575
00:31:17,510 --> 00:31:18,606
I believe I've heard enough.

576
00:31:18,630 --> 00:31:20,186
I want you and your team
to go over his data,

577
00:31:20,210 --> 00:31:21,256
see if there's anything to it.

578
00:31:21,280 --> 00:31:24,276
If there is, come up with a
list of possible solutions.

579
00:31:24,300 --> 00:31:25,300
- I'd be glad to.

580
00:31:27,190 --> 00:31:28,340
- Thank you, gentlemen.

581
00:31:34,130 --> 00:31:37,426
- You're an alarmist, Peter,
just like the old man.

582
00:31:37,450 --> 00:31:40,566
Still, that was quite a
presentation you made back there.

583
00:31:40,590 --> 00:31:43,476
The extinction of every
living thing on this planet,

584
00:31:43,500 --> 00:31:44,756
compelling!

585
00:31:44,780 --> 00:31:47,036
Oskar Vallian write that for you?

586
00:31:47,060 --> 00:31:48,293
- You're not even going to
review my data, are you?

587
00:31:48,317 --> 00:31:50,426
- Oh no, I'll review it.

588
00:31:50,450 --> 00:31:51,746
I'll review it very carefully

589
00:31:51,770 --> 00:31:54,446
and prove that your little
theory is complete crap.

590
00:31:54,470 --> 00:31:55,666
And the amazing thing here is

591
00:31:55,690 --> 00:31:58,141
that by doing that, I'll
be doing you a favor.

592
00:31:58,165 --> 00:31:59,677
- How's that?

593
00:31:59,701 --> 00:32:01,606
- Have you forgotten what tends to happen

594
00:32:01,630 --> 00:32:03,746
