00:40:53,171 --> 00:40:55,316
- Symbolic, huh?

751
00:40:55,340 --> 00:40:57,053
Hanging in limbo.

752
00:40:58,310 --> 00:41:01,453
- It's an interesting concept,
wedding ring purgatory.

753
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:06,516
I wanted to apologize for
what I said the other day

754
00:41:06,540 --> 00:41:08,956
about your marriage, it
was none of my business.

755
00:41:08,980 --> 00:41:11,316
There's this really serious
genetic condition in my family

756
00:41:11,340 --> 00:41:13,616
called foot in mouth disease.

757
00:41:13,640 --> 00:41:15,146
- You oughta get that looked at.

758
00:41:15,170 --> 00:41:17,636
- Sorry, I was just trying to help.

759
00:41:17,660 --> 00:41:19,176
- It's not that I don't appreciate it,

760
00:41:19,200 --> 00:41:20,809
it's just that

761
00:41:20,833 --> 00:41:22,636
I don't know if my failed marriage

