775
00:42:01,810 --> 00:42:02,810
I screwed up.

776
00:42:03,690 --> 00:42:04,990
- You really want it back?

777
00:42:06,330 --> 00:42:08,136
- Nothing makes very
much sense without her,

778
00:42:08,160 --> 00:42:10,160
but I haven't figured out how to fix it.

